<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently (RC1) there is no way to set the parameters of Zend\Mvc\View\Http\RouteNotFoundStrategy.
The strategy is created without using config parameters (unlike the ExceptionStrategy) in the ViewManager.</p>

<p>Enabling exceptions is very helpful for debugging puposes.</p>

